2 Using theCrag





<p>You can start using theCrag straight away.</p>
<p>As you browse the index you'll discover a wealth of information about crags and routes all around the world. All of this is built from the contributions of our members and others. Read on for more information about some of the charts and data used in the index.</p>
<ul>
	<li><a href="/article/DifficultyBand">Grade Band charts</a></li>
	<li><a href="/article/Styles">Route Styles</a></li>
	<li><a href="/article/Seasonality">Seasonality charts</a></li>
	<li><a href="/article/CragGuru">Crag Guru</a></li>
</ul>
<p>When you're ready to start logging your ascents and contributing to the index you'll need to <a href="/article/Signup">create an account</a>.</p>

